OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FLiz Carr calls for theatres
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto host facemask-only      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fperformances               
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Actress Liz Carr has suggested theatres
OL,6, consider hosting separate performances 
OL,7, of shows for audiences who still want  
OL,8, to wear facemasks or socially distance.
OL,10,FThe Silent Witness star won best       
OL,11,Fsupporting actress at Sunday's Oliviers
OL,12,Ffor her role in The Normal Heart.      
OL,14,FAs live audiences have mostly abandoned
OL,15,Fwearing masks, Carr suggested venues   
OL,16,Fcould offer "Covid-safer" performances.
OL,18,F"Theatre should remain accessible even 
OL,19,Fto those of us who have health         
OL,20,Fconditions," she told BBC News.        
